#   2. Secure the .env file by restricting permissions:
#        chmod 600 .env
#   3. Set ownership so only your user can access it:
#        chown <user>:<user> .env
#   4. Edit ".env" and replace all placeholder values with
#      secure production-quality secrets before deploying.
#
# NOTE:
